name: Redirector
description: Browser extension (Firefox, Chrome, Opera, Edge) to redirect urls based on regex patterns, like a client side mod_rewrite.
readme_summary: The Redirector browser extension allows users to redirect URLs based on defined regex or wildcard patterns, functioning as a client-side mod_rewrite. It supports multiple browsers and provides examples for common use cases like de-mobilizing websites, escaping doubleclick tracking, redirecting AMP pages, and customizing DuckDuckGo !bangs.
key_features: URL redirection based on regex patterns
Browser extension support (Firefox, Chrome, Opera, Edge)
primary_use_case: Redirecting URLs based on regular expression or wildcard patterns in web browsers.
cover_image_prompt: A skilled traffic controller in a futuristic city, directing streams of data packets (URLs) through a network of glowing tubes. The controller uses a console with regex patterns to reroute packets based on their content, sending them to different destinations. Some packets are diverted from a chaotic highway to a smooth, efficient route. Small screens display snippets of regex code and URL examples. The scene is set at night with neon lights and a sense of organized chaos. The image should be in a 3D isometric illustration style with vibrant colors and crisp details.

name: bambot
readme_summary: Bambot is a project focused on providing open-source designs for low-cost AI robots. The repository aims to enable users to build and experiment with AI robotics. It emphasizes accessibility and affordability in the field of AI robot development.
primary_use_case: Playing with and developing open-source, low-cost AI robots.
cover_image_prompt: A friendly robot assembling smaller AI robots on a workbench, surrounded by open-source components and tools. The larger robot is powered by a visible AI core, represented by glowing circuits and data streams. The smaller robots are diverse in design, showcasing their adaptability. A subtle UI screen in the background displays code snippets and robot schematics. The scene is set in a brightly lit, modern workshop with a clean and organized aesthetic. The image should be in a 3D isometric illustration style with vibrant colors and clear details.
